MINING RIGHTS AND CONCESSIONS
Peru:
We have 159,430 hectares in concessions from the Peruvian government for our exploration, exploitation,
extraction and production operations, at various sites, as follows:
    Toquepala    Cuajone    Ilo    Other    Total
 (hectares)
