As part of the settlement of claims brought on behalf of the Company and its shareholders against Grupo
Mexico, AMC and certain current and former directors (together with Grupo Mexico and AMC, the
‘‘Defendants’’) a dividend of $0.44428 per share was paid on February 21, 2019 to shareholders of record
at the close of business on February 11, 2019, other than the Defendants. The settlement dividend,
